ygData.messageBody:
Wish I could of been there, whenever I hit a hell
level (in lvl 35 now) I usually switch to my lower gyus
for a while since lvling slows down with my wizzie.
My other chars are all roaming around the 10th lvl
(War, Pal, Mag, Dru). Once I get my PC set up at my
friends house (long story short, we are moving and
staying with some friends) I'll be on more. He has cable
so it will be cool for EQ and my other on-line games
(Mostly RogueSpear) to have the high speed connection.
Hope to see you all on-line
soon.<br><br>Jonquil<br><br>PS I have been visiting other EQ clubs that I am a
member of (and joining a few new ones) and threw our
club name out there, hopefully we will get more
members to join and the club will be hoppin again!
